OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780578664
OL,3,CDJ Carl Cox on his love of the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT and why he supports Michael
OL,5,CDunlop
OL,7,F"That first experience was will," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"It was quite scary to begin with,
OL,11,Fbecause your sense are just not ready
OL,12,Ffor that. Eventually you get used to
OL,13,Fit, but for your first time you
OL,14,Fliterally step back.
OL,16,F"You can feel the kinetic energy
OL,17,Fthat's built up around the speed of
OL,18,Fthese bikes - it's the sensation of it
OL,19,F- and that doesn't get old at all."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780578664
OL,3,CDJ Carl Cox on his love of the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT and why he supports Michael
OL,5,CDunlop
OL,7,FRiders race at speeds of up to 200mph,
OL,8,Fon what are usually public roads for
OL,9,Fmost of the year, but closed for two
OL,10,Fweeks of qualifying and racing around
OL,11,Fthe world-famous Mountain Course.
OL,13,FNot content with prowling around the
OL,14,Fpaddock, and simply watching on as a
OL,15,Ffan, Carl Cox also manages his own
OL,16,Fteam in 'Carl Cox Motorsport'.
OL,18,FA proud sponsor of the most successful
OL,19,Frider of all time, Michael Dunlop, in
OL,20,Fan unlikely friendship that grew from
OL,21,Fa shared love of motorsport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780578664
OL,3,CDJ Carl Cox on his love of the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT and why he supports Michael
OL,5,CDunlop
OL,7,FCarl said: "We come from two different
OL,8,Fworlds, but once we sat down together
OL,9,Fwe found that we had a lot in common
OL,10,Fwith a lot of things in life.
OL,12,F"But he'd never really experienced the
OL,13,Fmusic side of my life, so I invited
OL,14,Fhim to come to a few parties of mine
OL,15,Fand he loved it, so outside of him
OL,16,Fbeing so focused with road racing, he
OL,17,Fspeaks to me about things outside of
OL,18,Fit, which enriches him as a person,
OL,19,Fand I find him really endearing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780578664
OL,3,CDJ Carl Cox on his love of the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT and why he supports Michael
OL,5,CDunlop
OL,7,F"A lot of people get Michael wrong in
OL,8,Fthe way that he is as a person, but
OL,9,Fpeople don't realise the concentration
OL,10,Fand everything you need to do what
OL,11,Fthey're doing, at the level that
OL,12,Fthey're doing it, Michael's
OL,13,Fconcentration is at the highest level.
OL,15,F"He's like everyone - they want to
OL,16,Fwin, they want to be on the step, they
OL,17,Fwant to be involved, they want to
OL,18,Finspire others - and people do really
OL,19,Fappreciate the efforts that these guys
OL,20,Fput in to their road racing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780578664
OL,3,CDJ Carl Cox on his love of the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT and why he supports Michael
OL,5,CDunlop
OL,7,FCarl now has a property on the 37.73-
OL,8,Fmile course, giving him a front row
OL,9,Fseat to the road racing action.
OL,11,F"If anyone's a biker, they get to
OL,12,Funderstand that even though you might
OL,13,Fthink that you're fast, the Isle of
OL,14,FMan TT sorts out the wheat from the
OL,15,Fchaff, 100%.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780578664
OL,3,CDJ Carl Cox on his love of the Isle of
OL,4,CMan TT and why he supports Michael
OL,5,CDunlop
OL,7,F"And the reason why these guys and
OL,8,Fgirls are where they are, is because
OL,9,Fthey have the ability to do that in
OL,10,Fsuch a way, which it goes beyond it
OL,11,Fhuman understanding, especially my own
OL,12,Funderstanding.
OL,14,F"There's no way I'll be able to do
OL,15,Fwhat I do in the at the, at the pace
OL,16,Fthat they do that, but at the end of
OL,17,Fthe day, they see it as fun. And
OL,18,Fthat's what it should be all about."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
